beer.beer_name: Wet Wet Wet Hop Pale Ale
beer.beer_description: A “hoppy” American Pale Ale that uses fresh Chinook and Centennial hop cones harvested from Ryefield Hops & brewed on the same day. The fresh hops accentuate the pure lupulin, providing a bouquet of pine and citrus alongside a grassy dankness depth that you can only get in a wet hop brew.
